                },
                {
                  "text": "3.0 \\times / 2\\mathrm{yrs}",
                  "bbox": [
                    45,
                    49,
                    301,
                    193
                  ],
                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": ", while both the DRAM and interconnect bandwidth have been increasingly falling behind, with a scaling rate of ",
                  "bbox": [
