                  "text": " over the same time period, respectively. With these trends, memory — in particular, intra/inter-chip memory transfer — will soon become the main limiting factoring in serving large AI models. As such, we need to rethink the training, deployment, and design of AI models as well as how we design AI hardware to deal with this increasingly challenging memory wall.",
