              "type": "text",
              "text": "Selective occlusion of tumor blood vessels, to deprive tumors of nutrients and oxygen and start an avalanche of tumor cell death, is an attractive strategy for combating cancer[9-13]. Vascular occlusion can exert its effects within hours following the rapid induction of",
              "line_count": 1,
              "page_size": [
                594,
                783
