              ],
              "type": "text",
              "text": "thrombus formation in tumor vessels, and carries a decreased risk of resistance development. Moreover, vascular occlusion is a strategy that can be used for many types of cancer, as all solid tumor-feeding vessels are essentially the same^{11,12}.",
              "line_count": 1,
              "page_size": [
