                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": ", the tube-shaped DNA nanorobot was non-covalently closed along a defined seam (Fig. 1a and Supplementary Fig. 11). We confirmed the closed and open states of the DNA nanorobot by atomic force microscopy (Fig. 1b). The four bright spots on the surface of the origami sheet represent the raised height produced by the thrombin cargo.",
