                39,
                60,
                292,
                82
              ],
              "type": "text",
              "text": "nanorobot is able to change its structure in response to target cells, and that the exposed thrombin payload can induce coagulation.",
              "line_count": 1,
              "page_size": [
                594,
                783
              ],
              "spans": [
                {
                  "text": "nanorobot is able to change its structure in response to target cells, and that the exposed thrombin payload can induce coagulation.",
                  "bbox": [
                    39,
                    60,
