                  ],
                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": ". Tumors in mice receiving targeted nanotube-Th grew slightly slower than did tumors in mice receiving saline, free thrombin, empty nanorobots or nontargeted nanotube-Th (Fig. 3g-i). Treatment with targeted nanotube-Th slightly increased animal survival to ",
