                    226
                  ],
                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": " (Fig. 3j). The weak inhibitory effect presumably correlates with its modest thrombogenic activity in tumor vessels, as evidenced in tumor sections (Supplementary Fig. 23a). The nanorobot-Th proved to be even more effective in a B16-F10 melanoma mouse model (Fig. 4a,b), in which three out of eight of the mice receiving nanorobot-Th showed complete regression of the tumors. The median survival time of the mice was extended from 20.5 to ",
