                },
                {
                  "text": " increase in tumor growth during this period of treatment. Collectively, these data show that our targeted thrombin delivery system based on a reconfigurable DNA nanostructure exhibits promising in vivo antitumor efficacy, and is applicable to tumors of diverse levels of vascularization.",
