                  "text": ") (Supplementary Fig. 26), suggesting the DNA nanorobot system is immunologically inert, which is in accordance with previous observations[8,21,28]. The nanorobot-Th also did not cause any observable cytotoxicity in standard CCK-8 cell proliferation assays (Supplementary Fig. 27).",
