                },
                {
                  "text": " streptomycin. The murine melanoma cell line B16-F10 was grown in RPMI 1640 medium supplemented with ",
                  "bbox": [
                    39,
                    59,
                    292,
                    140
                  ],
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "10\\%",
                  "bbox": [
