                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": " (8-10 months old, half male and half female) were also used in the study. All pigs were healthy and maintained in the animal facility at the Farm Animal Research Center (Beijing, China) under standard conditions prescribed by the Institutional Guidelines. The study protocol was approved by the Institutional Animal Care and Use Committee of the Institute of Zoology, Chinese Academy of Sciences.",
                  "bbox": [
