                  "text": " mice were fed with doxycycline diet since the 6th week after birth to induce primary lung adenomas. After being induced for 2 weeks, mice with tumors were randomly divided into four groups (three animals per group) and treated with saline, free thrombin, nontargeted nanotube-Th or nanorobot-Th, respectively, by intravenous injection once every ",
