              "type": "text",
              "text": "injections (n = 3 mice). Mouse serum was obtained by centrifuging whole blood taken by retro-orbital venous puncture at different time points. Serum cytokine concentrations including IL-6, IP-10, TNF\\alpha (R&D Systems, China, Shanghai, China, SM6000B, SMCX100, SMTA00B) and IFN\\alpha (ThermoFisher Scientific, Shanghai, China, KMC4011) were measured by ELISA as per the manufacturer's protocol using 50~\\mu \\mathrm{l} serum^{34-37}.",
