              ],
              "type": "text",
              "text": "5'-FITC-AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAACTAAAGTTTGTCGTGAATTGCG-3'and 5^{\\prime} -GTAAAGCTTTTTTTTTTTTTTTTTTTTTTTT TTTTT-BHQ1-3'.",
