              "type": "text",
              "text": "Staining of tissues. For histological examination, tumors and major organs were collected from MDA-MB-231-bearing nude mice at the indicated time points post-administration of DNA nanorobot-Th and various controls. Tissue samples were fixed in 4\\% paraformaldehyde, immunostained with anti-CD41 antibody for thrombosis or anti-CD34 antibody for endothelial",
