              "type": "text",
              "text": "Blinding. All experimental procedures and quantification of results, including injections, isolation of the tumors or organs, tissue histological analysis and FACS, were done by two independent researchers.",
              "line_count": 1,
              "page_size": [
                594,
                783
              ],
              "spans": [
                {
                  "text": "Blinding. All experimental procedures and quantification of results, including injections, isolation of the tumors or organs, tissue histological analysis and FACS, were done by two independent researchers.",
