                  "text": " using an Eppendorf thermal cycler (Eppendorf Mastercycler ep Gradient S, Hamburg, Germany). Unless otherwise stated, all DNA strands or aptamers were purchased from the oligonucleotide synthesis service of Invitrogen (Invitrogen, Carlsbad, CA).",
