              ],
              "type": "text",
              "text": "HUVECs were prepared and blocked with goat serum as described above. Serum-starved HUVECs where surface nucleolin expression was downregulated were also used. Non-starved and serum-starved cells were incubated with DNA nanorobots labeled with fluorophore-quencher fasteners for 2\\mathrm{h} at 37^{\\circ}\\mathrm{C}. Cells were washed twice with PBS and assayed using flow cytometry.",
