              "type": "text",
              "text": "Preparation of thrombin-DNA conjugates and thrombin activity analysis. Thrombin-DNA conjugates were prepared using sulfosuccinimidyl-4-(N-maleimidomethyl) cyclohexane-1-carboxylate (sulfo-SMCC, Sigma-Aldrich,",
              "line_count": 1,
              "page_size": [
                594,
                783
              ],
              "spans": [
                {
                  "text": "Preparation of thrombin-DNA conjugates and thrombin activity analysis. Thrombin-DNA conjugates were prepared using sulfosuccinimidyl-4-(N-maleimidomethyl) cyclohexane-1-carboxylate (sulfo-SMCC, Sigma-Aldrich,",
                  "bbox": [
                    39,
                    700,
                    292,
                    732
