                  "text": "25^{\\circ}\\mathrm{C}",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": " at a steady rate of ",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "10\\mathrm{min} / {}^{\\circ}\\mathrm{C}",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": " using an Eppendorf Mastercycler. Excess dye-modified DNA was removed using ",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "100\\mathrm{kD}",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": " centrifugal filters. A 20-fold molar excess of fasteners and a fivefold molar excess of targeting strands, including the AS1411 sequence, were subsequently added. The mixture was heated to ",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "37^{\\circ}\\mathrm{C}",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": ", then cooled to ",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "15^{\\circ}\\mathrm{C}",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": " at a rate of ",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "10\\mathrm{min} / {}^{\\circ}\\mathrm{C}",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": " to promote assembly.",
                  "bbox": [
                    299,
                    550,
                    553,
                    650
                  ],
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "page_idx": 7,
              "bbox": [
