                  "text": "Cell surface expression of nucleolin. The expression of nucleolin on the cell surface was assessed with antibodies specific to human nucleolin using a Beckman Coulter CyAn ADP flow cytometer (Fullerton, CA, USA). HUVECs were trypsinized, washed twice in PBS, resuspended in ",
