              "type": "text",
              "text": "A 20-fold molar excess of recombinant nucleolin was added and incubated with DNA nanorobots labeled by fluorophore-quencher fasteners at 37^{\\circ}\\mathrm{C}. Fluorescence intensity measurements were performed with a fluorescence spectrometer (LS55, Perkin Elmer).",
              "line_count": 1,
              "page_size": [
                594,
