                  "text": ". Then the cells were stained with DIO (plasma membrane) and DAPI (nucleus) (Sigma-Aldrich, St. Louis, MO) and imaged with a Nikon Ti-e microscope equipped with an UltraVIEW Vox confocal attachment (Perkin Elmer, Boston, MA, USA).",
