              ],
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Cell culture. All cell lines were purchased from the American Type Culture Collection (Manassas, VA, USA) unless stated otherwise. The human breast cancer cell line MDA-MB-231, and human umbilical vein endothelial cells (HUVECs) were maintained in DMEM supplemented with 10\\% FBS, 100\\mathrm{U / ml} penicillin and 100~\\mathrm{U / ml} streptomycin. The human ovarian cancer cell line SK-OV3 (Shanghai Institutes for Biological Sciences, Shanghai, China) was maintained in McCoy's 5A medium supplemented with 10\\% FBS, 100~\\mathrm{U / ml}",
