                    90,
                    551,
                    180
                  ],
                  "type": "inline_equation"
                },
                {
                  "text": " for a total of six treatments. The day of the first injection was designated day 0. Tumors were measured with calipers in three dimensions. The following formula was used to calculate tumor volume: Volume = length ",
                  "bbox": [
                    298,
                    90,
                    551,
                    180
                  ],
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "\\times",
