                  "text": "For manuscripts utilizing custom algorithms or software that are central to the paper but not yet described in the published literature, software must be made available to editors and reviewers upon request. We strongly encourage code deposition in a community repository (e.g. GitHub). Nature Methods guidance for providing algorithms and software for publication provides further information on this topic.",
                  "bbox": [
                    26,
                    101,
                    542,
                    131
                  ],
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            },
